{"id":273007,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/南周官微发布致歉信-编辑部罢工抗议/","date":"2013-01-06T14:19:45Z","modified":"2013-01-07T03:29:52Z","title":"南周官微发布“致歉信 ” 编辑罢工抗议","content":"<p>6日21时许南方周末新浪微博官方帐号发布一则简短道歉信，道歉信中称，南周新年献词系一编辑草拟，非网络传闻所说的宣传部长庹震，以下为道歉信全文：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e9%81%93%e6%ad%89/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273010\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273010\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/南周道歉.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/南周道歉.jpg 587w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/南周道歉-300x219.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这一说法显然过于牵强，难以被采信。 此条道歉信发布后，南周编辑部通过ID@<a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/2042731401\" target=\"_blank\">南方周末经济</a> 发布了一篇声明，声明中称南方周末受到有关方面压力，所发布的内容不代表编辑部态度，呼吁上级组织尊重事实，停止干预。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/79c19b89gw1e0k62ujqykj-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273011\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273011\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/79c19b89gw1e0k62ujqykj-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/79c19b89gw1e0k62ujqykj-1.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/79c19b89gw1e0k62ujqykj-1-300x277.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">与此同时，南方周末微博编辑吴蔚发微博透露，自己已经向新媒体业务总经理上缴了南方周末官方微博的密码，上级已经取消了自己对官方帐号的管理权限，自己将不对帐号所发内容负责。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273012\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273012\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/微博.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/微博.jpg 591w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/微博-300x91.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px\" /></a></p>\n<p>南方周末编辑张华声称，目前南方周末部分编辑已罢工，即将发布联署声明。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273014\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273014\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/罢工.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/罢工.jpg 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/罢工-300x204.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">@文三娃：在这里，读懂中国。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/89676c4djw1e0k6ldy2roj/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273020\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273020\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/89676c4djw1e0k6ldy2roj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"419\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/89676c4djw1e0k6ldy2roj.jpg 419w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/89676c4djw1e0k6ldy2roj-300x257.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 419px) 100vw, 419px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">@褚朝新：泣告：褚朝新，南方周末记者。本报蒙难，已进入非常状态，本人即时起宣布暂时停止正常工作，与诸同事共赴报难。报社恢复正常，即恢复工作。另，南方周末新浪官方微博被强行收缴，今日起至恢复正常期间不能代表我们南方周末采编员工。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/gonggao/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273024\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273024\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/gonggao.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/gonggao.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/gonggao-300x126.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">@南方周末经济：这是我们的《共同声明》，请大家迅速扩散。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/a_7-070cuaaiqxt/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273030\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273030\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/A_7-070CUAAIQXt.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"1182\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/A_7-070CUAAIQXt.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/A_7-070CUAAIQXt-381x1024.jpg 381w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">部分媒体发布“内涵晚安帖”声援。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/68b1c43btw1e0kanx0rcuj/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273090\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273090\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/68b1c43btw1e0kanx0rcuj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/68b1c43btw1e0kanx0rcuj.jpg 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/68b1c43btw1e0kanx0rcuj-487x1024.jpg 487w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">@hsin747 ：南方周末新聞職業倫理委員會凌晨聲明。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/5392eee7gw1e0kfkpbux4j/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273109\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273109\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/5392eee7gw1e0kfkpbux4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"2444\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/5392eee7gw1e0kfkpbux4j.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/5392eee7gw1e0kfkpbux4j-54x300.jpg 54w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/large-16/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273147\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273147\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/large.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"4040\" /></a></p>\n<p>@南方无周末中国没新闻：谢谢大家，我们依然站着！</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%e5%8d%97%e5%91%a8%e5%ae%98%e5%be%ae%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89%e4%bf%a1-%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%a2%e5%b7%a5%e6%8a%97%e8%ae%ae/%e5%8d%97%e6%96%b9%e6%97%a0%e5%91%a8%e6%9c%ab%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e6%b2%a1%e6%96%b0%e9%97%bb/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273111\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-273111\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/@南方无周末中国没新闻.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/@南方无周末中国没新闻.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/@南方无周末中国没新闻-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18269,19168,20534],"tags":[21765,8948,9540,9000,9212]}